entity.name: TEST ECT: After six new cases Wuhan plans to test all 11 million residents

text:
Wuhan plans to test all 11 million residents after detecting 6 new cases of #COVID19, its first in a month. The tests will occur over a 10-day period, says Chinese state media.

The U.S. — with the most cases worldwide — has yet to test 10 million people. https://t.co/2C3BpqrovW
